### 0️⃣ Clear old test data (optional, for clean testing)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/testing/clear
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 1️⃣ Create a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@trackit.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### 2️⃣ Create a new company
POST http://localhost:5000/companies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company_name": "Acme Ltd",
  "industry": "Fintech",
  "country": "Rwanda",
  "company_size": "50-100",
  "website": "https://acme.com",
  "contact_person": "John Doe",
  "contact_email": "john@acme.com",
  "contact_phone": "+250788123456"
}

###

### 3️⃣ Assign a new onboarding
POST http://localhost:5000/onboarding
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company_id": 1,
  "assigned_to": 1,
  "status": "contacted",
  "notes": "Reached out via email"
}

###

### 4️⃣ Update the onboarding record
PUT http://localhost:5000/onboarding/7
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "assigned_to": 1,
  "notes": "Followed up via phone"
}

###

### 5️⃣ Get all onboarding records
GET http://localhost:5000/onboarding

###

### 6️⃣ Get dashboard
GET http://localhost:5000/dashboard


